
Beautifly	 A bug type Pokémon

BEAUTIFLY’s favorite food is the sweet 
pollen of flowers.  If you want to see 
this POKéMON, just leave a potted flower 
by an open window.  BEAUTIFLY is sure 
to come looking for pollen. 

